{"tid":837089,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《屍殺列車》開拍荷李活版 《詭屋驚凶實錄》導演溫子仁加盟","createTime":"2018-09-26T06:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T14:15:05.000Z","uid":212249,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3f5e13236bfdc959ed44b3b52f8dcba96ff901","tid":837089,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"由孔劉、馬東石、鄭有美等人主演嘅韓國賣座喪屍電影《屍殺列車》，前年上映時席捲全球，早前導演延尚昊更宣佈開拍《屍殺列車》嘅續集《半島》。今日再傳來消息，指《屍殺列車》有機會開拍荷李活版本。<br />\n<br />\n據知有5間電影公司競標，包括New Line、Universal、Paramount、Lionsgate及Screen Gems，最後由New Line拿下版權，而荷李活版《屍殺列車》將由《詭屋驚凶實錄》導演溫子仁（James Wan）擔任製片及《詭娃安娜貝爾》嘅Gary Dauberman擔任編劇，目前暫未知荷李活版本嘅《屍殺列車》幾時開始製作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180926/58724225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58724225&d=GLlPsK05qGU%2FIJO3gfn48u9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=d2ce215a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58724225&h=e1380c84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180926/58724225</a>"},{"pid":"6faf0ed6893037954c5d938bda343c7c6bac849d","tid":837089,"uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05d69a88bed0bc9c53d842e5612f4706374d6dd","tid":837089,"uid":78773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"又溫子仁"},{"pid":"9a06871a0030d5f409b36564e0cc3daf8fd88d85","tid":837089,"uid":137569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c05d69a88bed0bc9c53d842e5612f4706374d6dd","tid":837089,"uid":78773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"又溫子仁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"唔係導演<br 